    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .a {className: a;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Шартномани бекор қилиш ҳақидаги келишув</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Шартнома тузилган сана</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">{#4}Шартнома рақами</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Келишув тузилган жой </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Бундан буён матнда “Буюртмачи” деб юритилувчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">{#16}Ташкилот номи </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">номидан Устав асосида иш юритувчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">{#17}Мансабдор шахс лавозими</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">{#18}Мансабдор шахс Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span>бир томондан, ҳамда бундан буён матнда “Ижрочи” деб юритилувчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">{#21}Ижрочи ташкилот номи </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span>номидан иш юритувчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">{#22}Мансабдор шахсининг лавозими</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">{#23}Мансабдор шахсининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">иккинчи томондан</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">қуйидагилар ҳақида мазкур Келишувни туздилар.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">1. </span><span class=\"structures structure-25\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#25}Шартнома бекор бўлиш сабаби</span> <span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">сабабли томонлар </span><span class=\"structures structure-26\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#26}Буюртмачи ва ижрочи ўртасида тузилган шартнома санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">кунидаги </span><span class=\"structures structure-27\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#27}Буюртмачи ва ижрочи ўртасида тузилган шартнома рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> сонли </span><span class=\"structures structure-28\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#28}Буюртмачи ва ижрочи ўртасида тузилган шартнома предмети ёки номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> шартномасини бекор қилишга қарор қилдилар.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">.<span class=\"leading\"></span>Мазкур келишув тарафлар имзолаган вақтдан эътиборан кучга киради ва шартнома шу вақтдан бекор қилинган деб ҳисобланади.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">3. </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Томонларнинг юқорида айтиб ўтилган Шартнома буйича мажбуриятлари мазкур Келишув кучга кирган вақтдан бошлаб тугатилади.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Томонларнинг ижро этилиши бошланган мажбуриятлари қуйидаги тартибда ижро этилади:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"structures structure-29\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#29}Томонларнинг мажбуриятларини ижро қилиш тартиби кўрсатилади</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">. Шартнома бекор қилиниши муносабатлари бекор қилинар экан, шартнома тарафларида бир-бирларига нисбатан ҳеч қандай эътироз ва талаб бўлмайди.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">5.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> Мазкур Келишув бир хил юридик кучга эга бўлган икки нусхада тузилиб, томонларнинг ҳар бирига бир нусхадан берилди.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 48px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">6.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> Томонларнинг адреслари, банк реквизитлари ва имзолари</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 48px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 48px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">БУЮРТМАЧИ</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">ИЖРОЧИ</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 49px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Манзил:</span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Буюртмачининг манзили</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Манзил: </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Ижрочининг <span class=\"leading\"></span>манзили</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 48px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">СТИР:</span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Буюртмачининг СТИР рақами</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">СТИР: </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Ижрочининг СТИР рақами</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 48px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#17}Мансабдор шахс лавозими</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#22}Мансабдор шахсининг лавозими</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 48px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#18}Мансабдор шахс Ф.И.О.</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#23} Мансабдор шахсининг Ф.И.О.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 48px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Буюртмачининг <span class=\"leading\"></span>ҳисоб рақами</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Ижрочининг ҳисоб рақами</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 48px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Буюртмачининг МФО рақами</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Ижрочининг банк коди МФО</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 48px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12